entry.title: ajillepalli/HandsOnCyberTutorials
entry.summary:
#HandsOnCybersecurityTutorials In this repository you will find the complete LaTeX source for hands-on cybersecurity tutorials. Funded by the U.S. National Science Foundation (NSF) and the State of Idaho IGEM program.

Tutorials List:

  • Encryption With OpenSSL
  • The Art of Secure Web Browsing
  • Static Testing: Static Analysis and Code Reviews
  • Group Policy with Active Directory (2 Parts)
  • Network Firewalls (2 Parts)
  • Social Engineering
  • Network Scanning with Nmap and Netcat
  • Password Security (2 Parts)
  • Penetration Testing
  • Silver and Golden Tickets
  • Social Engineering
  • Firewall Management
  • Virtual Networks
  • Vulnerability Scanning
  • Web Application Security
  • WireShark Fundamentals
